Subject - common itnerface for RealSubject and Proxy
a proxy can be used anywhere a RealSubject is expected


proxy - clients interact with real subject through proxy

proxy can access even delete real subject.

Subject is running on remote machine

Subject is expensive to create and you want to creaty it only when you want


remote proxies - encodes request for sending request to real subject running on different adress space
has authority to do something in authority of client